<p>Mentions revisions [in <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>, 2d ed.].</p> 
            <p>Argues with FG’s theory of heredity, defending Pangenesis: "I cannot doubt that every unit of the hybrid is hybridised and sends forth hybridised gemmules."</p>
